          "description": "Dr. Poostchi was very patient and thorough and spent over four hours with me doing a lot of work. She was cognizant of my struggle to become numb and was interested in making sure I was comfortable and waited till I was fully numb before proceeding with the work. She was detail-oriented, patient, and listened. I highly recommend her. It wasn\u2019t cheap (more expensive than my regular dentist), but I think the quality of the work and the level of care was better and made it worth it. The space is nice. No windows, but it still has a good ambiance and was pretty relaxing and quiet. Not busy at all on a weekday afternoon.",
