          "description": "THE BEST DENTAL PRACTICE IN THE WORLD! I was so traumatized from my previous dental experience from other practices. But the second I walked into Wall Street Dental Spa I can tell just by the good energy in the office that I was going to be well taken care of. The moment I walked in I was immediately attended to. I was brought in by one of the sweetest assistants named Tiffany, she really changed my mind about dentistry and made me feel comfortable and relaxed. She introduced me to the infrared PEMF mat in the operator's and I was so relaxed I almost took a nap lol. The best dental and spa treatment ever. The chair that I was sitting in even had massage feature. I almost didn't want to leave lol. The hygienist was amazing Tina did such a job with my cleaning, I felt no pain at all. When Dr. Leon introduced herself to me I immediately felt safe. She went over detail with me with such care and passion she really made understand dentistry more. She saved my teeth! The office is so beautiful esthetic. I can't wait to go back for my next cleaning!",
