          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWRdL8b3BnmqeffMGr2_y_E4KpK7fQcBLiV7qUHWjs1SamXPhIkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "This has been the best dental experience I\u2019ve had in NYC, and I truly don\u2019t see myself going anywhere else. From the moment I walked in, the atmosphere was welcoming and comfortable.\n\nJose was incredibly warm, friendly, and knowledgeable. He took the time to explain everything and made the entire visit feel easy, and the cleaning was completely pain-free.\n\nDr. Berwick was just as kind and thorough. She really took the time to assess my situation, walk me through next steps, and make sure I felt informed and at ease.\n\nI\u2019ve been looking for a dental office that combines excellent care with genuinely warm, friendly people, and this is exactly that. You never feel like just another patient here. Highly recommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKa1VtbHRRelZSWkVKUlZ6RnVZVVZqWmxoMWJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x75ffb990d55e0408!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjJkUmltQzVRZEJRVzFuYUVjZlh1bnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
